    "Background": {
      "text": "Usually complications of\nsinusitis\n(especially frontal, ethmoidal, or sphenoidal) or\notitis media\nOther causes include other ear infections,\ncranial trauma\nor surgery, or rarely\nbacteremia\nIn children <5yo, cause is typically bacterial meningitis\nTypically due to epidural abscess extending into subdural space to cause subdural empyema",
