    "Evaluation": {
      "text": "Assess for alternative causes of symptoms (e.g. labs to rule out metabolic process, glucose, infectious workup)\nMRI brain\nwith contrast\nBlood cultures\nDefinitive diagnosis by culture of surgical specimens\nLP\nNOT\nhelpful and may precipitate herniation\nIn infants, a subdural tap may be diagnostic and may relieve pressure",
